Package gpp.model.languageparser.python

Class PythonLanguageParser

java.lang.Object
gpp.model.languageparser.LanguageParser
gpp.model.languageparser.python.PythonLanguageParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGeneralLanguageParser, IGeneralLanguageParserConditional, IGeneralLanguageParserExpression, IGeneralLanguageParserFlow, IGeneralLanguageParserLoop, IPythonLanguageParser
public class PythonLanguageParser
extends LanguageParser
implements IGeneralLanguageParserConditional, IGeneralLanguageParserLoop, IGeneralLanguageParserExpression, IGeneralLanguageParserFlow, IPythonLanguageParser
Clase que se encarga de parsear ficheros Python.
